  <num>5-123.02</num>
  <heading>Use of unnecessary or wanton force.</heading>
  <text>Any officer who uses unnecessary and wanton severity in arresting or imprisoning any person shall be deemed guilty of assault and battery, and, upon conviction, punished therefor.</text>
